videos.description: Alex Starzyk punt for 35 yds, downed at the SFla 32
videos.headline: Temple's line drive punt

videos.description: Quinton Flowers scrambles left and then right, buying himself enough time to find Marquez Valdes-Scantling wide open in the end zone for the 27-yard touchdown putting USF up 7-3.
videos.headline: Flowers buys plenty of time, then fires opening TD for USF

videos.description: Temple caps off a 15-play drive by leaking out Colin Thompson who is wide open for Phillip Walker to find for the one-yard touchdown pass putting Temple back in front at 10-7.
videos.headline: Temple misdirection leaves Thompson wide open for TD catch

videos.description: After falling behind to Temple, USF answers right back on a 31-yard touchdown pass from Quinton Flowers to Tyre McCants capping off an eight-play drive in only 2:03 to go up 13-10.
videos.headline: USF answers in a hurry with 31-yard strike
Blocked extra point nearly returned by Temple

videos.description: After needing 15-plays to find the end zone on the last drive, Temple finds pay dirt after only two plays when Ryquell Armstead goes 76 yards to put the Owls back in front 17-13.
videos.headline: Temple back in the end zone when Armstead goes 76 yards in a flash

videos.description: Phillip Walker pass complete to Ventell Bryant for 36 yds to the SFla 18 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: Temple's Bryant makes sideline catch after review

videos.description: Quinton Flowers run for 50 yds to the Temp 34 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: Q. Flowers run for 50 yds for a 1ST down

videos.description: Quinton Flowers finishes off a speedy 3-play, 84-yard drive by going right up the middle on the keeper to give USF the lead back at 23-20.
videos.headline: Flowers goes untouched up the middle for 20th career rushing TD

videos.description: After getting a short field with a blocked punt, Temple punches it in with another rushing touchdown, this one from Jahad Thomas from nine yards out to increase the Owls' lead to 34-23.
videos.headline: Temple continues to find the end zone with the running game

videos.description: Marlon Mack gets through the line and finds pay dirt from 30 yards out for his 10th rushing touchdown of the season to pull USF to within seven points of Temple midway through the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Mack's 10th rushing TD of season trims Temple's lead

videos.description: Brett Kean pass intercepted Delvon Randall return for 21 yds to the SFla 22 SOUTH FLORIDA Penalty, Personal Foul (-3 Yards) to the SFla 3
videos.headline: B. Kean pass intercepted,D. Randall return  for 21

videos.description: Temple turns a late USF turnover into seven more points, this time with a three-yard run from Jahad Thomas to make it 44-30 late in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Temple increases lead late to solidify upset bid

videos.description: Brett Kean sacked by Romond Deloatch for a loss of 5 yards for a SAFETY
videos.headline: B. Kean sacked by R. Deloatch for -5 yds for a SAFETY
